      <li>Neeche apni company ka naam click karen aur us page par jayein</li>
      <li>Apna 14-digit number enter karen aur <strong>Check Bill</strong> button dabayein</li>
      <li>Aapka poora bill 3-5 seconds mein screen par aa jayega</li>
      <li><strong>PDF Download</strong> button se bill save karen ya Print karen</li>
    </ol>

