    <h2>Bill Kaise Pay Karen — Online Tarike</h2>
    <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:2.5;">
      <li><strong>JazzCash:</strong> Bill Payments → Electricity → LESCO/MEPCO/etc → 14-digit reference number dalein → Confirm</li>
      <li><strong>EasyPaisa:</strong> Bill Payments → Bijli → Company select karen → Reference number → Pay</li>
      <li><strong>Bank App (HBL/MCB/Meezan):</strong> Bill Payments → Electricity → Company → Account number</li>
      <li><strong>1-Link ATM:</strong> Bill Payment → Biller Code → Reference number → Pay</li>
      <li><strong>Bill par QR Code:</strong> Kisi bhi bank app se QR scan karen — instant payment</li>
    </ul>

